Class Task

java.lang.Object
Task
Record Components:
title - Title of the task.
description - Description of the task.
startDate - Uses MyDate to create a start date for the task.
completedDate - Uses MyDate to create a completed date for the task.
dueDate - Uses MyDate to create a due date for the task.
startTime - Uses Time2 to create a start time for the task.
completedTime - Uses Time2 to create a completed time for the task.
dueTime - Uses Time2 to create a due time for the task.
taskCompleted - A boolean control variable used to set the task completion status.
Direct Known Subclasses:
CompoundTask, SimpleTask
public abstract class Task extends Object
